      now. '
    backgroundName: 
  - speaker: Mouse
    portraitName: Mouse_Neutral
    text: 'Let''s go find stuff we can organize while she''s still rehearsing. '
    backgroundName: 
  - speaker: Mouse
    portraitName: Mouse_Neutral
    text: 'How about the props box we saw earlier while organizing the boxes? It''ll
